#23500
The Garden Gates~
   A towering set of pewter gates shines with a light dusting of moisture.  
The sounds of birds and rustling foliage give a peaceful feeling for the lush
green space beyond.  Stretching to the east and west is a wall of immensely
thick shrubs standing as tall as the gates.  The view beyond the gates is
blurry due to a light, but ever-present mist.  
~
