#23501
A Cobblestone Path~
   Round, grey stones line the path ahead providing solid footing among the
disorienting mist.  Strange colored birds fly back and forth among the tops of
the shrub wall, seemingly unperturbed by the presence of strangers.  The path
leads north and south while nothing of interest lies perpendicular.  
