A Cobblestone Path~
   Fruit bearing trees can be seen all around with enticing low-hanging
branches.  Though unseen, the chatter of various fauna can be heard from the
canopy.  A slight breeze wafts sweet scents through the area though the mists
remain unmoved.  In the dirt beside the path various tracks can be made out
with both small and large markings, many of which were made in haste.  
