#23523
Water's Edge~
   At the edge of the pond, the water appears crystal clear.  With a clean
view of the bottom, gentle slopes of dirt are broken up by stray rocks,
aquatic plants, and broken limbs.  Small fish dart around chasing even smaller
prey and water insects dance above on the surface.  The thorny bush walls
encircling the gardens leave no room to walk around the pond, the only way
forward is to dive right in.  
~
