#23535
A Half Burned Copse~
   The green and lively garden comes to an abrupt halt as the surrounding
plant life is speckled with burning embers and small streams of smoke.  Warm
air flows from the back of the room towards the cobblestone pathway as it
looks to escape the rising heat.  For now the creeping fire appears to be kept
at bay by an unseen force.  
~
