#23583
A Quiet Pond~
The water is crystal clear, and if not for the apparent depths, one might
see straight to the bottom.  Small fish and freshwater mammals can be seen
darting around the lively depths, chasing after their next meal.  Cool to the
touch, the water brings a refreshing feeling in the otherwise humid environment.
~
